     H            Y.                                    1
     FAFAPP60 IF  E           K        DISK
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@ZETI  4
     C                     PARM           P@TEHI  3
     C                     PARM           P@FLG   1
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@FLG
      *
     C                     MOVE P@ZETI    K@ZETI  4
     C                     MOVE P@TEHI    K@TEHI  3
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@ZETI
     C                     KFLD           K@TEHI
      *
     C           KEY       SETLLAFAPP60
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY       READEAFAPP60                  88
     C   88                LEAVE
     C                     MOVE '*'       P@FLG
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
